item.content:encoded:
In 2011 we had the dream of building a world-class animation studio where aspiring artists could study and work together towards pioneering an Animated Motion Picture Industry in Trinidad and Tobago.
Our vision garnered support through the 2012 Idea to Innovation competition, a joint initiative of The Council for Competitiveness and Innovation and The Ministry of Planning and the Economy, as we were selected to be amongst the 50 winning ideas. This set us firmly along the path towards making our dream a reality.
Now, three years later, we provide professional 3D Animation services, as well as, a comprehensive training programme in 3D Character Animation.
In all that we do, we strive to uphold the values expressed in our vision and mission, thereby ensuring that our clients and students receive the very best of service.
